Fading in background.
@bgf("bg/bg1")

Adding a sprite.
--Each call to img(f) adds a new sprite
@local i = imgf("arm01m", "c") --"c" is the sprite slot, valid values: "l", "lc", "c", "rc", "r"

Changing background image.
@bgtween("bg/bg2")

Changing character image.
@imgtween(i, "arm01l")

Color-tinting the character image (fuchsia)
@i:setColor(1.0, 0.0, 1.0)

Fading away and deleting sprite.
@rmf(i)

Fading away and deleting background.
@rmbgf()
